[Details are awaited of the precise relationship of this strain of Ebola
virus to the strains isolated previously in the Sudan and elsewhere in
Africa. A preliminary report (see: Acute hemorrhagic fever - Sudan (W
Equatoria) (02) 20040521.1369) suggested that a milder form of disease
might be associated with this strain. - Mod.CP]
